### ==========================================
### user-app.http
### Test Auth + Users + Addresses qua API Gateway
### Yêu cầu: chạy gateway + user-app, đã cấu hình keys/ cho JWT
### Sử dụng http-client.env.json (chọn môi trường 'local' trong VS Code)
### ==========================================

@gateway = {{gatewayUrl}}
@userEmail = user-{{$timestamp}}@example.com
@userPassword = Test@123456

### 1) REGISTER - Đăng ký tài khoản mới (role mặc định: CUSTOMER)
# @name registerUser
POST {{gateway}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}",
  "fullName": "HTTP Test User"
}

###

### 2) LOGIN - Lấy accessToken/refreshToken
# @name loginUser
POST {{gateway}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

###

@userToken = {{loginUser.response.body.accessToken}}

### 3) ME - Lấy thông tin user hiện tại
# @name me
GET {{gateway}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

@userId = {{me.response.body.id}}

### 4) USERS - Get by ID (auth-only)
GET {{gateway}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 5) USERS - List all (ADMIN only) - với token CUSTOMER sẽ 403 (minh họa)
GET {{gateway}}/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 6) USERS - Update profile (auth-only)
PUT {{gateway}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "HTTP Test User - Updated",
  "phone": "0912345678"
}

###

### 7) ADDRESSES - List của user (auth-only, userId lấy từ token bởi Gateway)
GET {{gateway}}/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 8) ADDRESSES - Create (auth-only, Gateway tự gán userId từ JWT)
# @name createAddress
POST {{gateway}}/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "phone": "0912345678",
  "street": "123 Lê Lợi",
  "ward": "Bến Nghé",
  "district": "Quận 1",
  "city": "TP.HCM",
  "isDefault": true
}

###

@addressId = {{createAddress.response.body.id}}

### 9) ADDRESSES - Update
PUT {{gateway}}/addresses/{{addressId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn A - Đổi tên",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "street": "456 Nguyễn Huệ"
}

###

### 10) ADDRESSES - Set Default
PUT {{gateway}}/addresses/{{addressId}}/set-default
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 11) ADDRESSES - Delete (tuỳ chọn)
# DELETE {{gateway}}/addresses/{{addressId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###